Ksyusha 

You can get some inspiration by looking through our photos, filled with the idea: SHINE BRIGTH NO MATTER WHAT.

Kristy helps her special twins with oil pastel drawings. Also, you may check the jewelry with the prints of the girlsâ€™ drawings.

Take a look at young artists and Kristy, and feel shining bright no matter what!
